er-oura-rukako-suspends-talent-activities-indefinitely-and-becomes-a-774inc-nanashiinku-management-staff-member/">VTuber Ruka Oura无限期暂停艺人活动，以“Nanashinku管理人员”身份活跃</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Oura Rukako 无限期暂停人才活动，并以“Nanashinku 管理人员”的身份活跃起来” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-oura-rukako-suspends-talent-activities-indefinitely-and-becomes-a-774inc-nanashiinku-management-staff-member/embed/#?secret=y6vuC9vq6f#?secret=gQrGpDOqyY" data-secret="gQrGpDOqyY" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="通知｜大浦流香子 // Nanashi Link" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1o_VQ8PH0r0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="iyemc647347af9426e" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
