务必核对人才本人、所属单位、集团或公司提供的一手信息，感谢您告知。</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://youtube.com/@Rukako_Oura" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Rukako Channel / Ruka Oura [Nanashinku]</a> / <a href="https://twitter.com/Rukako_Oura" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Ruka Oura <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f989.png" alt="🦉" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> NANASHINK</a> /<a href="https://www.774.ai/talent/rukako-oura" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">大浦流香子</a></p><cite>YouTube / 推特 / Nanashinku</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp 管理代表“No.2（临时）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙 VTuber 信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-oura-rukako-streaming-was-hit-slanderous-comments-such-as-774inc-nanashiinku-is-a-noob-and-it-would-be-hilarious-if-they-were-absorbed-by-nijisanji-etc/">VTuber Rukako Oura 发表了诸如“Nanashinku 无能”和“如果 Nijisanji 吸收它会很有趣”之类的诽谤性评论或</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/vtuber-oura-rukako-streaming-was-hit-slanderous-comments-such-as-774inc-nanashiinku-is-a-noob-and-it-would-be-hilarious-if-他们被 nijisanji-etc/feed/ 吸收了0 92881
